title: Honey-Can-Do HMP-03770 Knockdown Bamboo Hamper Instruction Video
description: Instruction video for assembling your new Honey-Can-Do HMP-03770 knockdown bamboo hamper

asset.author: myhoneycando
asset.description: Instruction video for assembling your new Honey-Can-Do HMP-03770 knockdown bamboo hamper

transcripts: at honey can do we are your source for organization storage and style we make product assembly easy so that well anyhow you can do it to begin remove product contents and group all like parts locate the two frame pieces and notice that they have recessed holes on one side which when assembled will face outward join the two frame pieces reset toes outward using the four horizontal poles and hex screws like this and tighten the screws using the hex wrench now cover the heads of each screw using the bamboo plugs by simply pushing them into place like this next open the cloth bag and placing flaps upward lower it into the frame and attach it by wrapping the flaps around the frame and snapping them into place then snap the flats at the bottom of the bag around the lower horizontal now place the cloth bottom in the bottom of the bag and voila your knockdown bamboo hamper is ready to receive all of your dirty laundry dirty clothes never looked so good happy organizing at honey can do we don't believe you have to go broke to have a beautiful well-organized home and assembly should be easy to do
